{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/keywordselect/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Ian Chu","author":"Ian Chu","siteUrl":"https://ianccy.com","social":{"facebook":"chu1228"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"dfae05d1-663f-5c41-aa2a-7287d51f9b9b","fields":{"slug":"/2019-02-keywordselect/"},"headings":[{"value":"選擇關鍵字方法","id":"選擇關鍵字方法","depth":2},{"value":"google adword","id":"google-adword","depth":3},{"value":"google search","id":"google-search","depth":3},{"value":"規劃內容","id":"規劃內容","depth":2},{"value":"標題非常重要","id":"標題非常重要","depth":2},{"value":"完成內容後","id":"完成內容後","depth":2},{"value":"持續修改優化","id":"持續修改優化","depth":2},{"value":"心得","id":"心得","depth":2}],"excerpt":"從去年剛開始寫 blog，就一直很想分享的內容，以前曾擔任過行銷，主要是負責 seo 優化，有一些些小技巧跟心得想分享。以前是依靠寫文章，並且在文章內導購手法，記得那時候部門內的全部 blog、官網我都有負責，到最後整體網站流量都還不錯，官網、blog 都成長非常多。 先不說廢話了，接下來分享如何使用 google…","html":"<p>從去年剛開始寫 blog，就一直很想分享的內容，以前曾擔任過行銷，主要是負責 seo 優化，有一些些小技巧跟心得想分享。以前是依靠寫文章，並且在文章內導購手法，記得那時候部門內的全部 blog、官網我都有負責，到最後整體網站流量都還不錯，官網、blog 都成長非常多。</p>\n<p>先不說廢話了，接下來分享如何使用 google adword 關鍵字分析工具。</p>\n<h2 id=\"選擇關鍵字方法\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E9%81%B8%E6%93%87%E9%97%9C%E9%8D%B5%E5%AD%97%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95\" aria-label=\"選擇關鍵字方法 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>選擇關鍵字方法</h2>\n<p>假設你希望網站搜尋流量能成長，我會比較推薦用文章來吸流量，這方法相對容易，寫一篇跟跟你產品有正相關的文章，再引導到購買頁面。</p>\n<p>首先我們要先列出、定義，什麼是我們需要的關鍵字，還有產品調性符合的關鍵字。</p>\n<h3 id=\"google-adword\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#google-adword\" aria-label=\"google adword permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>google adword</h3>\n<p>google 關鍵字有個搜尋量預估的工具，可以告訴你每月大概有多少人搜尋這個關鍵字，註冊 adword 後可以免費使用。</p>\n<p>網址 : <a href=\"https://goo.gl/3WAtQM\" title=\"google adword\">google adword</a></p>\n<p>\n  <figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"margin: 7vw 0;\">\n  \n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7604c974d5b5bce2d612c1fec6811a4d/acfc1/keywordtool.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 37.57575757575758%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/7604c974d5b5bce2d612c1fec6811a4d/a805d/keywordtool.webp 495w,\n/static/7604c974d5b5bce2d612c1fec6811a4d/6ec60/keywordtool.webp 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/7604c974d5b5bce2d612c1fec6811a4d/b3db0/keywordtool.png 495w,\n/static/7604c974d5b5bce2d612c1fec6811a4d/acfc1/keywordtool.png 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n          src=\"/static/7604c974d5b5bce2d612c1fec6811a4d/acfc1/keywordtool.png\"\n          alt=\"keyword tool\"\n          title=\"keyword tool\"\n          src=\"/static/7604c974d5b5bce2d612c1fec6811a4d/acfc1/keywordtool.png\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n      </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n  <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">keyword tool</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n      </p>\n<p>點擊關鍵字規劃工具，再點擊<code>尋找新的關鍵字</code>，輸入<code>雨衣</code>關鍵字後，可以看到月搜尋流量，還有更多相關的字詞(僅參考用)。</p>\n<p>\n  <figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"margin: 7vw 0;\">\n  \n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7c6f683cfa0ab1361b17f902e728a7b9/0a9e9/keywordtool2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 773px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 76.16161616161617%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/7c6f683cfa0ab1361b17f902e728a7b9/a805d/keywordtool2.webp 495w,\n/static/7c6f683cfa0ab1361b17f902e728a7b9/b5f3a/keywordtool2.webp 773w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 773px) 100vw, 773px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/7c6f683cfa0ab1361b17f902e728a7b9/b3db0/keywordtool2.png 495w,\n/static/7c6f683cfa0ab1361b17f902e728a7b9/0a9e9/keywordtool2.png 773w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 773px) 100vw, 773px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n          src=\"/static/7c6f683cfa0ab1361b17f902e728a7b9/0a9e9/keywordtool2.png\"\n          alt=\"keyword tool\"\n          title=\"keyword tool\"\n          src=\"/static/7c6f683cfa0ab1361b17f902e728a7b9/0a9e9/keywordtool2.png\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n      </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n  <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">keyword tool</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n      </p>\n<p>從上表我們可以看出雨衣是一個有搜尋量的關鍵字，還有其他相關字有雨鞋、雨傘、雨具等等，這些都先列出放到旁邊。</p>\n<h3 id=\"google-search\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#google-search\" aria-label=\"google search permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>google search</h3>\n<p>再來我們打開無痕 chrome，在 google 輸入雨衣，再來檢視 google search 下拉選單的推薦字詞。這邊可以看到有雨衣推薦、雨衣兩件式。這邊出現的字詞，你也可以用 adword tool 輸入看看月搜尋量。</p>\n<p>\n  <figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"margin: 7vw 0;\">\n  \n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/270e03e0a5aa06bb5daa09bc83ed0212/acfc1/search_rain.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 37.57575757575758%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/270e03e0a5aa06bb5daa09bc83ed0212/a805d/search_rain.webp 495w,\n/static/270e03e0a5aa06bb5daa09bc83ed0212/6ec60/search_rain.webp 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/270e03e0a5aa06bb5daa09bc83ed0212/b3db0/search_rain.png 495w,\n/static/270e03e0a5aa06bb5daa09bc83ed0212/acfc1/search_rain.png 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n          src=\"/static/270e03e0a5aa06bb5daa09bc83ed0212/acfc1/search_rain.png\"\n          alt=\"keyword search_rain\"\n          title=\"keyword search_rain\"\n          src=\"/static/270e03e0a5aa06bb5daa09bc83ed0212/acfc1/search_rain.png\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n      </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n  <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">keyword search_rain</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n      </p>\n<p>google 搜尋點擊網站進入，再返回上一頁，網站下方就會出現相關搜尋字詞的清單。</p>\n<p>\n  <figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"margin: 7vw 0;\">\n  \n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/9862a623639b40130a5166646ad6168a/acfc1/search_more.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 37.17171717171717%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/9862a623639b40130a5166646ad6168a/a805d/search_more.webp 495w,\n/static/9862a623639b40130a5166646ad6168a/6ec60/search_more.webp 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/9862a623639b40130a5166646ad6168a/b3db0/search_more.png 495w,\n/static/9862a623639b40130a5166646ad6168a/acfc1/search_more.png 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n          src=\"/static/9862a623639b40130a5166646ad6168a/acfc1/search_more.png\"\n          alt=\"keyword search_more\"\n          title=\"keyword search_more\"\n          src=\"/static/9862a623639b40130a5166646ad6168a/acfc1/search_more.png\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n      </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n  <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">keyword search_more</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n      </p>\n<p>直接滾到 google 搜尋底部，會直接列出相關搜尋。<br>\n<figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"margin: 7vw 0;\">\n  \n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/9c7af53be98132ea87a517a0af206036/acfc1/search_related.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 30.303030303030305%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAGCAIAAABM9SnKAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAAgUlEQVQY05WQXQrDIBCEc/+rNYQE0j4KFrW7oa2Jtq5N/IlH2A4MzMsHM9PVWp3bjNFCCCllKaWy1TV790F8IiLAQiH9BxtN07il1CocQ//WKsSYuDAAXee1hQXpNq8I5P3BhZUK02jbWK1Df3nd5fdhQs48uJVEpBjzvhdrf/zPTkovXvmLs1lNAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/9c7af53be98132ea87a517a0af206036/a805d/search_related.webp 495w,\n/static/9c7af53be98132ea87a517a0af206036/6ec60/search_related.webp 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/9c7af53be98132ea87a517a0af206036/b3db0/search_related.png 495w,\n/static/9c7af53be98132ea87a517a0af206036/acfc1/search_related.png 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n          src=\"/static/9c7af53be98132ea87a517a0af206036/acfc1/search_related.png\"\n          alt=\"keyword search_related\"\n          title=\"keyword search_related\"\n          src=\"/static/9c7af53be98132ea87a517a0af206036/acfc1/search_related.png\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n      </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n  <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">keyword search_related</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n      </p>\n<p>這兩邊也可以找到非常多的關鍵字詞。都可以先列起來。再挑出與你產品有相關的關鍵字，組成一篇完整的文章內容。</p>\n<h2 id=\"規劃內容\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%A6%8F%E5%8A%83%E5%85%A7%E5%AE%B9\" aria-label=\"規劃內容 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>規劃內容</h2>\n<p>一般來說，會抓 1 個流量大的關鍵字，後面再一起拉幾個有搜尋量，但競爭不激烈的長尾關鍵字，例如說 <code>一件式雨衣、雨衣推薦、年度字2019、ptt</code>之類的。因為一開始大流量字沒辦法有很好排名，通常都要依賴那些長尾關鍵字撐起流量，慢慢增加整體流量，最後大流量的關鍵字也一起成長排名。</p>\n<p>你整個內容架構，就可以圍繞雨衣一件式或兩件式、材質防水，新年度 2019 設計的雨衣，或是節錄出 ptt 網友推薦內容。</p>\n<p>從產品本身敘述到網友口碑推薦，由內往外、起承轉合架構出內容。有個重點就是，千萬不要剪貼簿東貼西貼別人內容，一來侵害著作權、二來搜尋通常不會太好，google 很喜歡原創內容。</p>\n<h2 id=\"標題非常重要\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%A8%99%E9%A1%8C%E9%9D%9E%E5%B8%B8%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81\" aria-label=\"標題非常重要 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>標題非常重要</h2>\n<p>到現在，title 還是非常重要…，所以好好拼湊好一段標題，例如說 <code>一件式雨衣，2019新款雨衣推薦</code>，這種標題雖然看似很芭樂，但是確實還滿有效果的。</p>\n<p>以前我自己推薦這個詞必做，會想辦法生內容，請使用者分享心得，在內容節錄一小段。</p>\n<p>desscription 描述要寫的人看得懂的，雖然他對排名沒有正相關，但你好好打，會吸引人搜尋點擊進來，間接影響點擊率、流量，</p>\n<h2 id=\"完成內容後\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%E5%85%A7%E5%AE%B9%E5%BE%8C\" aria-label=\"完成內容後 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>完成內容後</h2>\n<p>假設你今天內容完成，可以做哪些工作。首先可以發 facebook、社群分享、或是 email 等等，一來透過外部連結讓 google 能快速索引網站、二來增加網站被分享出去散播，進而增加流量的可能。簡而言之就是建立外部連結，這很難沒錯，可遇不可求。</p>\n<p>我自己心得是，網站的流量與 google 排名有絕對的正相關，以前會透過經營 ptt，分享知識型內容，導入流量，但這塊流量非常無感，排名幾乎不會變動。反倒是 facebook 流量幫助非常大，雖然 link 是 nofollow 的，通常一天導入 5000 流量後，排名會突然衝到第一頁，但這方法已經沒用了，後期一樣操作手法完全沒幫助排名了。</p>\n<h2 id=\"持續修改優化\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E5%84%AA%E5%8C%96\" aria-label=\"持續修改優化 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>持續修改優化</h2>\n<p>我從以前就很討厭<code>優化</code>這個詞，應該叫做隨時準備調整內容、標題方向，當你今天建立好內容後，你應該要利用 search console，持續觀察排名變化，還有透過 ga 了解這個網址，被訪問的流量結構，搜尋流量最珍貴，再來是推薦流量，直接流量次之(以上純個人看法)。</p>\n<p>過了一個月之後，成效還是非常差，這時候你要考慮改變方向，找其他競爭較小比較少人做的關鍵字，修改增減內容。</p>\n<p>但如果很幸運的，排名不斷的進步，你要知道是哪些關鍵字，或那部份的流量幫助成長，你就要小心修改內容去刪減到那部份的關鍵字，保持原本好的部分，刪減你現在沒做到的關鍵字的部分。</p>\n<h2 id=\"心得\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%BF%83%E5%BE%97\" aria-label=\"心得 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>心得</h2>\n<p>自己覺得剛開始做 seo，要成長流量很好做，因為從 0 開始，你隨便都能成長流量，但當你流量到一個程度後，要進一步成長，會變得很困難，你可以會挑戰業界最大量的關鍵字，例如 <code>日本旅遊</code>，那你要規劃得不再只是一頁內容，而是整體網站的串連操作。</p>\n<p>當你做到了，但要保持排名又是另一個學問了…。</p>\n<p>最後，以上都是我非常主觀的個人心得，警示一下有可能過舊沒用。如果有哪些錯誤，再麻煩提醒了。</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"SEO關鍵字分析選擇，優化工具介紹","date":"February 26, 2019","description":"從去年剛開始，就一直很想分享的內容，以前曾擔任過行銷，主要是負責seo優化，有一些些小技巧跟心得想分享。接下來分享如何使用google adword關鍵字分析工具等等，規劃架構出內容，幫助提升排名。","categories":"marketing","tags":["seo"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1.9767441860465116,"src":"/static/9df8d308625a497564d6e95a6ae4a753/ee604/google_search.png","srcSet":"/static/9df8d308625a497564d6e95a6ae4a753/c972b/google_search.png 340w,\n/static/9df8d308625a497564d6e95a6ae4a753/27625/google_search.png 680w,\n/static/9df8d308625a497564d6e95a6ae4a753/ee604/google_search.png 800w","sizes":"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"}}}},"timeToRead":5,"parent":{"__typename":"File","modifiedTime":"2021-04-03T11:16:59.783Z"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2019-02-keywordselect/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2019-02-promise/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Javascript Promise example 簡易實作模擬","tags":["javascript"]}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/2019-03-eventpass/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"JavaScript Capture Bubble DOM事件獲取&冒泡","tags":["javascript"]}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["1481458783","63159454"]}